form will be useful to avoid tedious typing. Notice the Null input at the \
end, which will be automatically converted to the default value.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1423013268,ExpressionUUID->"5de23a7f-e5c5-434a-975c-94171bbd18f0"],

